I"Ï<p>I grew up in <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anyue_County">Anyue</a> (known as <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pu_Prefecture_(Sichuan)">Puzhou</a> in Song Dynasty), Sichuan. Here there was a mathematician named <a href="https://mathshistory.st-andrews.ac.uk/Biographies/Qin_Jiushao/">Qin Jiushao</a> who gave the first constructive proof of the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chinese_remainder_theorem">Chinese Remainder Theorem</a>.</p>
